sudo apt-get update
sudo aptitude install mutt
sudo aptitude install getmail4
sudo aptitude install msmtp
sudo aptitude install proxychains

then configure ~/.muttrc:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/muttrc

configure ~/.msmtprc:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/msmtprc

configure ~/.getmail/getmailrc:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/getmailrc

configure your proxychains, /etc/proxychains.conf, for me it's like this:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/proxychains.conf

your alias file:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/alias

change the color theme mutt if you want, .mutt/colors:
https://github.com/Puqiyuan/Mutt_Getmail_Msmtp/blob/master/Config/colors

